snippet: Hurricane Sandy led to the cancellation of the first program of the Belcea Quartet’s Beethoven series at Zankel Hall, but Wednesday’s storm was not enough to keep the group from plunging into the rest of a formidable offering of late quartets.
abstract: James R Oestreich reviews concert of Beethoven works performed by Belcea Quartet at Zankel Hall.
lead_paragraph: Hurricane Sandy led to the cancellation of the first program of the Belcea Quartet’s Beethoven series at Zankel Hall, but Wednesday’s storm was not enough to keep the group from plunging into the rest of a formidable offering of late quartets.

headline.seo: The Belcea Quartet Plays Beethoven at Carnegie Hall
